<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<widget id="ph.com.divespot" version="0.0.2" versionCode="34" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/widgets" xmlns:gap="http://phonegap.com/ns/1.0" xmlns:cdv="http://cordova.apache.org/ns/1.0">
    <name>Divespot</name>
    <description>
        Divespot is an online social media portal intended for divers and for those who are interested in diving and underwater experiences. In Divespot, members have the opportunity to share their experiences by posting blogs, pictures, videos, etc. Members also have the opportunity to update their own profile and view others. This social media community enables them to share and connect with others who are of common interest. It also has a marketplace for the members to buy and sell items related to and necessary for diving.
    </description>
    <author email="admin@divespot.com.ph" href="http://divespot.com.ph">
        divespot.com.ph
    </author>
	
